comment:
* Prioritized list of callbacks to be performed once object graph has been
     * completely deserialized.

methods.name: void register(ObjectInputValidation obj, int priority) throws InvalidObjectException
methods.comment:
* Registers callback.  Throws InvalidObjectException if callback
         * object is null.

methods.name: void doCallbacks() throws InvalidObjectException
methods.comment:
* Invokes all registered callbacks and clears the callback list.
         * Callbacks with higher priorities are called first; those with equal
         * priorities may be called in any order.  If any of the callbacks
         * throws an InvalidObjectException, the callback process is terminated
         * and the exception propagated upwards.

methods.name: public void clear()
methods.comment: * Resets the callback list to its initial (empty) state.

methodNames: void register(ObjectInputValidation obj, int priority) throws InvalidObjectException
